title: Nine Inch Nails *LIVE*: Beside You In Time
description:
We're Back!!! After a long vacation, we're back with some stuff we had left over from the end of the year so, let's get to it.

Nine Inch Nails LIVE......Trent takes the gang on the road for one hell of a live show. Special effects, lights, explosions and a video wall (and a few thousand intimate friends) makes this one of the best of tours on video! If you weren't high before the show, you sure as hell feel like it afterwards.....  

Songs include "Head Like a Hole", "Beside You in Time", "Love is Not Enough", "You Know What You Are", "Terrible Lie", "Closer", "March of the Pigs", and more.


format: xvid, mp3
